<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>工作空间邀请</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'PingFang SC', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.4;
      color: #333;
      background: #f8f9fa;
      max-width: 460px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 12px;
    }

    .email-container {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      padding-bottom: 12px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
    }

    .title {
      color: #222;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .greeting {
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }

    .content-card {
      background: #f8fafc;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 16px 0;
      border: 1px solid #3b82f6;
    }

    .invitation-info {
      margin: 12px 0;
    }

    .info-item {
      margin: 8px 0;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #555;
    }

    .info-item strong {
      color: #333;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .accept-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #10b981;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 13px;
      margin: 12px 0 16px;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .note-text {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
      margin: 16px 0;
      padding: 10px;
      background: #f8f9fa;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding-top: 14px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #999;
      text-align: center;
    }

    p {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    p:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <!-- 头部 -->
    <div class="header">
      <h1 class="title">工作空间邀请</h1>
    </div>

    <!-- 问候语 -->
    <p class="greeting">您好！</p>

    <!-- 主要内容卡片 -->
    <div class="content-card">
      <p><strong>{{inviterName}}</strong> 邀请您加入工作空间：</p>

      <div class="invitation-info">
        <div class="info-item"><strong>工作空间：</strong>{{workspaceName}}</div>
        <div class="info-item"><strong>邀请人：</strong>{{inviterName}}</div>
        <div class="info-item"><strong>有效期：</strong>{{expiryHours}} 小时</div>
      </div>

      <a href="{{invitationUrl}}" class="accept-button">接受邀请</a>
    </div>

    <!-- 备注信息 -->
    <div class="note-text">
      <p>如果您不认识邀请人或认为这是误发的邮件，请忽略此邮件。</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 页脚 -->
    <div class="footer">
      <p>此邮件由 Monie 系统自动发送</p>
      <p>需要帮助？请联系 {{supportsEmail}}</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>